nodes.text: Quila was an aquatic planet in the galaxy. In 4 BBY, an Imperial freighter carrying Janard, a prisoner of the Empire, crashed into Quila's oceans. The rebels Sabine Wren, Ahsoka Tano, and Hera Syndulla mounted a rescue mission that led to a confrontation with Imperial forces in the partially-submerged freighter. A species of eel lived in the oceans of Quila.
